        <mxCell id="I2XxpJuBxpLWIYqSNJos-33" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;" value="- Пользователь заходит на страницу решения задачи&lt;div&gt;- Открывается websocket с LSP manager&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;LSP manager&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Проверка лимитов, подробнее в блоке ниже&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Создает под&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Ожидает Status.Phase ==&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;PodRunning |&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;PodFailed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- При PodPending &amp;amp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Unschedulable, cooldown на 1-2 секунды создание подов (должно быть редкий случай)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Проксирует соединение пользователя на&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;ws://{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;PodIP}:8080/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- При превышении maxPodCount вытесняем в следующем порядке&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- под без websocket подключений&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- самый старый под по CreatedAt&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- (можно позже подумать и переделать)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- При падении пода закрываем websocket с клиентом, реконнектом занимается клиент.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- При закрытии соединения со стороны пользователя ожидаем таймаут и удаляем под.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="400" width="396" x="384" y="730" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="I2XxpJuBxpLWIYqSNJos-34" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=7;" value="&lt;div class=&quot;pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;sticky bg-token-border-light&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative z-0 flex max-w-full&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;code-block-viewer&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; class=&quot;q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cm-scroller&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cm-content q9tKkq_readonly&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼn&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cm-content q9tKkq_readonly&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼn&quot;&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;Session&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼn&quot;&gt;struct&lt;/span&gt; {&lt;br&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;ID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;UserID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;LanguageServiceId&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;PodName&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;Status&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;  Connections []&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;Conn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;CreatedAt&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;time&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼn&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;Time&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cm-content q9tKkq_readonly&quot;&gt;LastActivityAt&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;time&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼn&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;Time&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cm-content q9tKkq_readonly&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cm-content q9tKkq_readonly&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼv&quot;&gt;sessions&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;ͼn&quot;&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;SessionID&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span class=&quot;ͼn&quot;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;Session&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cm-content q9tKkq_readonly&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;userSessions: map[UserID][]SessionID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cm-content q9tKkq_readonly&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;podToSession: map[PodName]SessionID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="300" width="270" x="30" y="720" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="LgDoCkQeRcNcNSYZ-bSp-23" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="MaxPodsPerUser - пользовательский лимит на число подов&lt;div&gt;MaxPodCreationsPerUserInMinute - польз лимит на количество запусков подов в минуту&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;MaxGlobalPods - глобальный&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;лимит на число подов&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;PodCreationRateLimit - лимит на параллельные createPod&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;MaxWaitQueueSize - если не укладывается в RateLimit, или в MaxGlobalPods, то ставим в очередь&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="110" width="340" x="20" y="1040" as="geometry" />
